| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0903 — Recovery Inhibition (coinbasecartel)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 85b3e286-707d-5f58-82ef-a1a493eb3b5d"
